Create a web site with a lot of users.
Website will have a few different pages.
One page will be for uploading images.
In order to upload photo(s), the user must enter their first and last name.
There will be a page for gallery, where the photos will all be displayed, right next to each other.
Under each photo, there will be the name of the person who uploaded it.

When the user clicks on a photo, the photo will be displayed in large format.